&kp LEFT_CONTROL  &kp GRAVE    &none      &none        &kp MINUS    &kp LPAR                &trans  &trans  &trans  &kp RPAR      &kp PLUS     &none         &none        &kp BSLH     &mt LC(DEL) DEL
&kp LEFT_SHIFT    &kp TILDE    &none      &none        &kp UNDER    &kp LBKT      &trans            &trans          &kp RBKT      &kp EQUAL    &kp COMMA     &kp DOT      &kp PIPE     &none
                                          &trans       &trans       &kp SPACE                                       &kp RET       &trans       &trans
