            bindings = <
&trans            &none  &none  &none   &none   &none                        &trans          &kp FSLH   &kp N7        &kp N8  &kp N9  &kp STAR  &trans
&kp LEFT_CONTROL  &none  &none  &none   &none   &none                &trans  &trans  &trans  &kp MINUS  &kp N4        &kp N5  &kp N6  &kp PLUS  &mt LC(DEL) DEL
